Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.56,0:00:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,A gust of wind came...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.80,0:00:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The thermos fell over...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.56,0:00:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The sandwiches were all dirty...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.00,0:00:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,At the time, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.17,0:00:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,just smiled sadly...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.45,0:00:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want one too, lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.16,0:00:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Franz!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.42,0:00:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.33,0:00:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.90,0:00:51.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.68,0:01:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Start walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.79,0:01:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.77,0:01:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.88,0:01:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get through to Mr. Verdeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.61,0:01:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I'm calling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.68,0:01:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, his wife just gave birth, so he's probably{\i}\N{\i1}still at the maternity center.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.69,0:01:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I've heard about you, Miss Eva Heinemann.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.36,0:01:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please, feel free to tell me anything you'd like.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.96,0:01:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.76,0:01:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}About what?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.70,0:01:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The testimony to prove Tenma's innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.57,0:01:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see. We're very grateful!{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.94,0:01:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}So...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.04,0:02:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}what hotel are you staying at right now?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.48,0:02:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Got it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.65,0:02:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll head over there right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:03.76,Title,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\pos(360,340)}The Escape
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,With timing like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.77,0:04:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll just go around me and keep driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.68,0:04:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The car comes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.08,0:04:21.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.08,0:04:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.42,0:04:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.92,0:04:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.82,0:04:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.22,0:04:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This timing should be right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.92,0:04:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.92,0:04:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.62,0:04:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.36,0:04:33.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- Comes.\N{\i1}- Hey.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.53,0:04:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Fall.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.96,0:04:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.86,0:04:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What? I'm in the middle of something.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.66,0:04:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really going to marry me today?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.24,0:04:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How many times do I have to tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.60,0:04:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.17,0:04:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You really will?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.21,0:04:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Swear to God?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.84,0:04:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll swear to anything you want today, Helene.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.78,0:05:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Then kiss me, Gustav.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.16,0:05:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's continue this in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.86,0:05:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.50,0:05:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Now's not the time for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.63,0:05:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You used my drugs again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.84,0:05:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the last of my stash!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.40,0:05:21.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.67,0:05:25.11,Default,,0,0,0,,No wonder your nose is running, bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.14,0:05:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm out here practicing for my job while\Nyou're in here snorting my stuff?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.98,0:05:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,What job? It's simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.65,0:05:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,All you're doing is lying in the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.22,0:05:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Simple?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.32,0:05:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Easy for you to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,If I mess up even a little, I'll die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.46,0:05:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.80,0:05:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.13,0:05:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be killed instantly
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.27,0:05:56.91,Default,,0,0,0,,- I don't want you to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.98,0:05:58.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- No, that was just an example...{\i}\N- I don't want you to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.44,0:06:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- No, that was just an example...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.01,0:06:03.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Gustav's gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.25,0:06:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There are still some things I have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.12,0:06:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.86,0:06:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotta have lots of kids with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.06,0:06:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to make a whole soccer team with our kids.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.57,0:06:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's so wonderful, Gustav.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.10,0:06:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be getting a load of cash from the job I'm about to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Then we'll get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.37,0:06:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll make my dream come true, right, Helene?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.01,0:06:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Gustav!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.68,0:06:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have them! I'll have them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.72,0:06:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have as many babies as you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.72,0:06:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep telling you, now is not the time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.52,0:06:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I want to make babies!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.76,0:06:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Be patient for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.56,0:06:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's almost time for a "Detective Forster" rerun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.10,0:06:55.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The car comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:56.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I jump out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.44,0:06:57.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I fall down.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.14,0:06:59.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The car comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.24,0:07:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I jump out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.57,0:07:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I fall down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.87,0:07:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The car comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I jump out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I fall down.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.91,0:07:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The car comes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.98,0:07:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm thinking of killing someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.72,0:07:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Your former fiancée...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva Heinemann.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.06,0:07:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.49,0:07:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.66,0:07:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.01,0:07:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so nice out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.72,0:07:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Such nice weather, yet I'm stuck in a car like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.92,0:07:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,With this damn serial killer, no less.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.86,0:07:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, I'm so unlucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.13,0:07:55.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop talking, Milch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're lucky.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.90,0:08:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,In this gloomy little prison van...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.43,0:08:04.47,Default,,0,0,0,,on your way to some dank detention facility...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,you get to hear plenty of stories about the twelve\Nescapes of the master escapee, Gunther Milch.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.21,0:08:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, which should I start with?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.01,0:08:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The one about how I escaped from\NKreiner Prison is the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.92,0:08:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.12,0:08:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. I'm just bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.66,0:08:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What time is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.69,0:08:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked you for the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's 9:32.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.14,0:08:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were out in the free world...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.44,0:08:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,it'd almost be time for a rerun\Nof "Detective Forster" on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.58,0:08:45.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you ever watch that show?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.05,0:08:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.78,0:08:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, it's almost time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:59.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna take care of this little job real quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.02,0:09:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You just watch me work from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.29,0:09:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,A gun...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.16,0:09:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you going to shoot it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.07,0:09:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just gonna use it to scare them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.93,0:09:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want our kids to have murderers for parents!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.14,0:09:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't shoot anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.74,0:09:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll even stop using drugs!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.08,0:09:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you, Helene.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.65,0:09:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I've really decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.65,0:09:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get married!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.06,0:09:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.76,0:09:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna live honestly from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.76,0:09:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't do jobs where I have to\Nwave a gun around anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.39,0:09:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.33,0:09:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.33,0:09:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing good comes from waving around things like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.60,0:09:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Gustav!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.40,0:09:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! This feels so great, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.81,0:09:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Helene!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.01,0:09:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.88,0:09:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you from the bottom of my...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.16,0:10:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.20,0:10:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.23,0:10:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,hit someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.90,0:10:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.37,0:10:23.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You... hit someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.44,0:10:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sit down, Milch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.38,0:10:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You... hit him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.08,0:10:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you hear me? Sit down, Milch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.12,0:10:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,That was probably my little brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.29,0:10:41.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The plan... failed, Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.13,0:10:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I taught Gustav the timing and\Nacting over and over again...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.83,0:10:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but in the end, nobody can do it as well as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.04,0:10:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked him to pass out on the road like he was sick...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.74,0:10:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,so he could stop the oncoming car...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.44,0:11:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,He's really bad, so you should've just\Navoided him and kept going...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.92,0:11:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,And yet... and yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.65,0:11:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,why did you have to go and hit him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.16,0:11:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't really get what you're saying, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,go check and see if it's someone you know or not!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.89,0:11:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Gustav...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.26,0:11:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Gustav...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.66,0:11:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Helene...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:11:58.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't good...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.77,0:12:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Is he still breathing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.14,0:12:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is really bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.44,0:12:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,E-Excuse me, but we have a doctor right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.82,0:12:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.82,0:12:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.94,0:12:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Gustav's dead...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.77,0:12:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.01,0:12:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,How could I have done this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.25,0:12:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I've totally failed...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.69,0:12:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Gustav!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.09,0:12:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.53,0:12:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe we should tell him to cover it up in the report...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.26,0:12:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How can we cover up something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.30,0:13:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I know, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.70,0:13:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The keys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.57,0:13:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the keys to the handcuffs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The keys!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.17,0:13:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the keys to the handcuffs!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.42,0:13:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you waiting for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:13:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.96,0:14:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you like anything to drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.53,0:14:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A Scotch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.30,0:14:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,No, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A cup of coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.34,0:14:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In our next story....{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.00,0:14:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A fire struck a large shopping mall in Dortmund today.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.94,0:14:20.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Thanks to the employees triggering the fire alarm,{\i}\N{\i1}the blaze was brought under control...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.35,0:14:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but two stores were completely lost.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.01,0:14:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- There have been no reported injuries.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.08,0:14:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- I thought I'd talk.{\i}\N{\i1}- There have been no reported injuries.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.02,0:14:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}About what?{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The testimony to prove Tenma's innocence.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.82,0:14:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Got it.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.02,0:14:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll head over there right now.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.49,0:14:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please wait in the hotel lobby.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.33,0:14:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to do by setting that man free?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.77,0:14:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,This just came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.54,0:14:51.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}At 10 o'clock this morning, in a suburb{\i}\N{\i1}of Düsseldorf, Erkrath...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.94,0:14:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}two prisoners who were being transported to the Hilden{\i}\N{\i1}Detention Facility escaped from police custody.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.45,0:15:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No details have been reported, but....{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.02,0:15:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the two fugitives who escaped were....{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.89,0:15:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gunther Milch, arrested for armored car robbery...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.93,0:15:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and the serial killer, Kenzo Tenma.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.20,0:15:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The police have been deployed...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.94,0:15:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and are now tracking down the two fugitives.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.45,0:15:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.45,0:15:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.82,0:15:37.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Mr. Verdeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.29,0:15:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I heard the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.43,0:15:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you have to escape?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.06,0:15:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.90,0:15:50.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Just when I was about to prove your innocence...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.23,0:15:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.90,0:15:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's no use asking me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.27,0:15:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand his motives either.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.84,0:15:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.44,0:16:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,For now, let's just head over to the police station.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.41,0:16:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.58,0:16:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,the truth is, there's something\Nthat I have to take care of first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.09,0:16:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.62,0:16:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Yes. That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.99,0:16:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We must both deal with the current situation calmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.53,0:16:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.93,0:16:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I completely agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.80,0:16:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That voice...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.37,0:16:28.04,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, we have to get the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.04,0:16:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.01,0:16:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That voice...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.24,0:16:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's exactly as you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.58,0:16:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- That voice...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.31,0:16:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Yes, as much as we can. Yes.{\i}\N{\i1}- That voice...{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.45,0:16:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Yes, as much as we can. Yes.{\i}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.08,0:16:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.04,0:17:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's your coffee...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.92,0:17:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not... my cigarette...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.13,0:17:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This smell...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.30,0:18:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that man's smell...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.57,0:18:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.88,0:18:16.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Roberto was just in this room!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.26,0:18:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Gustav!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.59,0:18:30.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Gustav's dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.93,0:18:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Helene, he's not dead yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.50,0:18:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But he can't be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.97,0:18:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He hit his head, and he's not bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.83,0:18:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,it's what they call a brain hemorrhage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.90,0:18:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that right, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand how you feel, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.58,0:18:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,we're going to change cars at the path through\Nthe forest up ahead, like we planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.85,0:18:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Gustav is just a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.65,0:18:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll leave him in this car.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.18,0:18:52.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.28,0:18:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,keep going!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.39,0:18:56.62,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have time to change cars.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.75,0:18:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You crazy?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.09,0:19:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The cops have seen this car.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.26,0:19:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll find us in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.49,0:19:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If we can get him to a hospital soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.16,0:19:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a chance he can be saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.90,0:19:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.40,0:19:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, your quick-wittedness saved my\Nescape plan when it was about to fail.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.47,0:19:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But from now on, you're going to listen to the pro.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.18,0:19:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel sorry for him, but we'll leave Gustav at\Nthe path through the forest up ahead and...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.98,0:19:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,keep driving to the hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.71,0:19:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Eisler Memorial Hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.19,0:19:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They have the best equipment\Nand staff in Düsseldorf there.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.66,0:19:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the hospital I worked at!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.62,0:19:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.26,0:20:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The main entrance to the hospital is just ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.86,0:20:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop crying!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.96,0:20:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you reach the entrance...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.20,0:20:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,tell them to give this letter to Dr. Wagner.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.37,0:20:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It contains a detailed description of the accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.94,0:20:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Gustav won't die?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.97,0:20:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He's still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.77,0:20:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up as long as he's still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.88,0:20:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.48,0:20:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.25,0:20:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,if we stick around here any longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.09,0:20:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,it's like we'll be asking to be found.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.23,0:20:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.16,0:20:45.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.90,0:20:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better stick with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.17,0:20:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a complete amateur at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.33,0:20:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The life of a woman I know is in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.74,0:20:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to get to her as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.74,0:20:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,A woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:21:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean to tell me that's why you escaped?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.45,0:21:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want women, just come with me to Tunisia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.08,0:21:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You can sleep with as many of\Nthe best women as you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.89,0:21:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.12,0:21:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.13,0:21:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.69,0:21:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't really killed anyone, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.37,0:21:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I shot one person...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.17,0:21:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,but he's still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.41,0:21:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.21,0:21:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,As far as that one goes, you're completely innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.81,0:21:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But you've got a real criminal record now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.78,0:21:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You're now officially a fugitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.89,0:21:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's meet up in Tunisia someday, fugitive to fugitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.16,0:21:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a great place!
